Sentencas: Cobalt doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-delta perovskite exhibits superior electrochemical performance when it was tested as an anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with high performance cobalt-doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ anodes

Sentencas: For the anode with a composition of Pr0.5Ba0.5Co0.25Fe0.75O3-delta-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-delta, the polarization resistance R-p was as low as 0.05 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C in air and 0.21 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C in 3% H2O-97% H-2.
Titulo: Intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with high performance cobalt-doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ anodes

Sentencas: In addition, this full-ceramic anode was tolerant to 50 ppm H2S and showed stable performance during the preliminary test.
Titulo: Intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with high performance cobalt-doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ anodes

Sentencas: The ceramic composite also exhibited superior activity for cathodic oxygen-reduction-reaction (ORR), thus enabled a symmetrical fuel cell.
Titulo: Intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with high performance cobalt-doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ anodes

Sentencas: In a lab designed full-ceramic symmetrical fuel cell, a power density of 0.75 Wcm(-2) at 750 degrees C has been achieved, demonstrating the superior properties of this oxide.
Titulo: Intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with high performance cobalt-doped Pr0.5Ba0.5FeO3-δ anodes
